What We Buy
In 1999, Royalty Clearinghouse started with a vision to simplify the process of buying and selling mineral rights, royalties and working interests. Since then, we've built an outstanding reputation as the trusted leader in oil & gas acquisitions. We've accomplished this by working with our customers in an open and friendly way. We help our customers evaluate their options and get the most value for their interests.




Sell Oil and Gas Mineral RightsSell Oil and Gas RoyaltiesSell Oil and Gas Working Interest









Where We Buy
While our roots are in Texas, we currently buy mineral interest all over the country. Royalty Clearinghouse owns minerals, royalties and non-operated working interests in most oil and gas producing basins in the lower 48 states. We also own non-producing minerals in selected areas. Areas of particular interest include: Texas, Oklahoma, New Mexico, Colorado, Kansas, Montana, Wyoming, North Dakota, California, Ohio, Illinois, Pennsylvania, Kentucky, West Virginia, Arkansas, and Louisiana.






